<i>On behalf of the Reno Airport staff,</i>

26:31.840 --> 26:34.592
<i>we'd like to wish you safe travels</i>
<i>and a merry Christmas.</i>

26:34.676 --> 26:37.429
<i>Thank you for flying with us,</i>
<i>and please, come again.</i>

